      <title>抵押债券投资者在市场动荡后获得了一些付款</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-05-03/cmbs-investors-get-some-payments-after-dustup-that-shook-market</link>
      <description><![CDATA[这一举动震惊了商业抵押贷款支持证券市场：该公司介入以结束一项与一家命运多舛的公寓企业相关的交易，该企业持有超过 1.6 亿美元的债券，债券持有人期望收回这笔交易。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-05-03/cmbs-investors-get-some-payments-after-dustup-that-shook-market</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 03 May 2024 13:15:00 GMT</pubDate>
