      <title>埃里安称“金发姑娘”就业报告取悦美联储和市场</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-05-03/el-erian-says-goldilocks-jobs-april-report-to-please-fed-markets</link>
      <description><![CDATA[Mohamed El-Erian 在美国 4 月份就业数据公布后表示，劳动力市场的降温应该会给美联储带来可喜的缓解，因为美联储希望让美国经济软着陆。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-05-03/el-erian-says-goldilocks-jobs-april-report-to-please-fed-markets</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 03 May 2024 13:14:42 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>日元上涨缓解了日本支撑受挫货币的压力</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-05-03/yen-strengthens-more-than-1-easing-intervention-speculation</link>
      <description><![CDATA[美国就业报告弱于预期，引发市场对美联储早些时候降息的押注，日元上涨，打压美元，缓解了日本可能再次介入市场支撑日元汇率的猜测。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-05-03/yen-strengthens-more-than-1-easing-intervention-speculation</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 03 May 2024 12:45:19 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>就业机会缺失后交易员推迟美联储降息，国债飙升</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-05-03/treasury-yields-tumble-as-jobs-data-revives-case-for-rate-cuts</link>
      <description><![CDATA[在美国劳动力市场报告落后于预期后，美国国债飙升，交易员加大了对美联储今年何时开始降息的押注。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-05-03/treasury-yields-tumble-as-jobs-data-revives-case-for-rate-cuts</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 03 May 2024 12:38:22 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>嘉能可集团接近收购壳牌新加坡炼油厂</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-05-03/glencore-backed-group-said-near-deal-for-shell-singapore-assets</link>
      <description><![CDATA[据知情人士透露，包括大宗商品贸易商嘉能可 (Glencore Plc) 和印度尼西亚化学品企业 PT Chandra Asri Pacific 在内的集团正在就收购壳牌公司 (Shell Plc) 在新加坡的资产进行深入谈判，交易价值可能约为 10 亿美元。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-05-03/glencore-backed-group-said-near-deal-for-shell-singapore-assets</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 03 May 2024 12:13:48 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>海军演习看到油轮驶出希腊湾关键海域</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-05-03/a-hotspot-for-russian-oil-transfers-is-suddenly-deserted</link>
      <description><![CDATA[在宣布在通常进行转运的地区进行海军演习后，从希腊南部海岸转运俄罗斯石油的油轮进一步驶入地中海。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-05-03/a-hotspot-for-russian-oil-transfers-is-suddenly-deserted</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 03 May 2024 11:43:32 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>随着战争风险消退，油价将出现二月以来最大单周跌幅</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-05-02/latest-oil-market-news-and-analysis-for-may-3</link>
      <description><![CDATA[由于中东地缘政治风险有缓解的迹象，而交易员继续权衡降息前景，油价创下2月份以来最大单周跌幅。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-05-02/latest-oil-market-news-and-analysis-for-may-3</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 02 May 2024 23:31:24 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>随着债券交易员重新加载美联储削减的赌注，股市上涨：市场结束</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-05-02/asian-stocks-to-rise-as-tech-lifts-wall-street-markets-wrap</link>
      <description><![CDATA[华尔街将美国就业市场放缓视为美联储最早将于 9 月开始降息的迹象，随着债券收益率暴跌，交易员大幅推高股市。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-05-02/asian-stocks-to-rise-as-tech-lifts-wall-street-markets-wrap</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 02 May 2024 22:31:30 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
